tspan.tspan: You can create your artwork using the
blank Artboard named "Your
Illustration" as a starting point.
Every Artboard contains
several elements. Each element has pre-made
assets of a specific subject. The
currently available sample asset
themes are:
- Heads
- Hairstyles
- Legs
- Hands
- Graphics
You can add the assets to your
Artboard by copying and pasting them
or by dragging & dropping them onto
the Artboard.
All asset shapes are fully editable; you
can modify the color and stroke
attributes or the shape's path in seconds.
Note: Some elements are grouped;
to access them, you might need, in
some cases, to select the group layer
to be able to access them!
Let your imagination loose, and have
fun creating!"
